===Format===
* '''Quarter Finals:''''' May 1st - 4th, 2025
** 64 teams, 2 matchdays.
*** 32 invited team.
*** 32 Underdogs team.
** Teams are divided equally into 4 groups of 16.
** Each group will play 6 matches in 4 days.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 8 team from each group (Total 32 teams)}} advance to Semi Finals
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Semi Finals:''''' May 5th - 8th, 2025
** 32 teams, 4 matchdays.
** Teams are divided equally into 4 groups of 8.
** Each group will play 12 matches in 4 days.
** Round-robin format.
** {{Bgcolortext|up|Top 16 teams}} advance to the Grand Finals
<div style="margin-top:12px"></div>
* '''Grand Finals:''''' May 9th - 11th, 2025
** 16 teams, 3 matchdays.
** 18 matches (6 each day).

